### Create habit
POST http://localhost:8080/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Read 10 pages"
}

### Create another habit
POST http://localhost:8080/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Workout"
}

### Get all habits
GET http://localhost:8080/habits

### Complete habit with ID 1 for today
POST http://localhost:8080/habits/1/complete

### Complete habit with ID 2 for today
POST http://localhost:8080/habits/2/complete

### Try completing habit 1 again
POST http://localhost:8080/habits/1/complete

### Get streak for habit 1
GET http://localhost:8080/habits/1/streak

### Get streak for habit 2
GET http://localhost:8080/habits/2/streak

### Test invalid habit
POST http://localhost:8080/habits/999/complete

### Test invalid streak
GET http://localhost:8080/habits/999/streak
